data.description: Welcome to your beautiful dream home tucked away in a private Ringgold neighborhood located right off the Interstate! This spacious residence is the epitome of southern living, boasting a multitude of enhancements for your comfort and enjoyment.  Upon entering the charming front porch, you will step in and discover a cozy atmosphere accentuated by a newly revamped fireplace wall, exuding warmth throughout the living space. To the left you will see french doors leading you out to your expansive screened in porch, freshly painted deck which then leads to the large, fully fenced in, backyard that is perfect for entertaining guests. Entering back into the house you must check out the spacious kitchen. With granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and a functional layout including an island. Upstairs your will find you primary suite and two generously sized bedrooms, connected by a jack and jill bathroom to provide maximum comfort and versatility. One of the great conveniences of this home is having a laundry room on the main level and an additional laundry closet upstairs which adds ease to your daily routine! As you head down to the basement you will find a great recreational room with endless opportunities and a full bathroom. If you are in need of storage look no further, the unfinished section of the basement has great storage opportunity, with additional space cleverly tucked away under the screened-in porch.  Other updates include new glass surrounding the front door and a newly installed fence for your large backyard, enhancing both aesthetics and functionality. If all that weren't enough, take life slow and enjoy the views of the sweeping mountains from your front porch. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful residence your own!
